1. Introduction
Welcome to TTSaver - Video Downloader ("we", "our", or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application TTSaver - Video Downloader (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect
2.1 Information You Provide
We do not require you to create an account or provide any personal information to use the App.

2.2 Information Collected Automatically
Device Information:
We may collect basic device information such as device model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers for the purpose of improving app performance and displaying advertisements.

Usage Data:
We collect anonymous usage data such as which features you use, how often you use the app, and download counts. This data is used solely to improve the App experience.

Clipboard Access:
The App accesses your device clipboard only to detect TikTok video links that you have copied. This is done locally on your device and the clipboard content is never transmitted to our servers.

3. Third-Party Services
3.1 Google AdMob
This App uses Google AdMob to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and use data to show personalized or non-personalized ads. This includes:

Device identifiers (Android Advertising ID)
IP address
Location data (approximate)
App usage information
You can learn more about how Google uses your data at:
https://policies.google.com/privacy

To opt out of personalized advertising, go to your device Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalization.

3.2 TikWM API (tikwm.com)
To download TikTok videos, the App sends the TikTok video URL you paste to the tikwm.com API. This is a third-party video parsing service. We do not send any personal data — only the video URL. Please review their privacy policy at https://tikwm.com.

4. Permissions Used
The App requests the following permissions:

Permission	Purpose
INTERNET	To fetch video data and download videos
ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE	To check internet connectivity
READ_MEDIA_VIDEO	To access saved videos in gallery
READ_MEDIA_IMAGES	To access saved images in gallery
READ_MEDIA_AUDIO	To access saved audio in gallery
WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE	To save downloaded files (Android 9 and below)
FOREGROUND_SERVICE	To run downloads in the background
POST_NOTIFICATIONS	To show download progress notifications
We do not access your camera, microphone, contacts, location, or any other sensitive data.

5. Data Storage
Downloaded videos, images, and audio files are saved directly to your device's local storage (Gallery/Downloads folder). We do not upload, store, or transmit any of your downloaded content to any server.

Your app preferences (dark mode, HD download, auto-paste) are stored locally on your device using Android DataStore and are never shared externally.

6. Children's Privacy
This App is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will delete such information.

7. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information collected through the App. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security of your data.

